FROM jruby:1.7

MAINTAINER opensource@groupon.com


RUN apt-get -q update && \
apt-get -q --no-install-recommends -q -y install git

RUN mkdir /app
WORKDIR /app

ADD Gemfile /app/
ADD Gemfile.lock /app/
RUN bundle install --without development torquebox

ADD . /app
